  "intent": "Execute automated distribution of PCR mastermix from a 12-well reservoir to a specified number of wells (up to 384) on a destination plate using a P20 multi-channel pipette. Aspirate user-defined volumes of mastermix from reservoir well A1 and dispense into sequential columns of the target plate, with optional tip reuse between transfers. Include touch-tip after each dispense and blow-out to waste reservoir well A2 when reusing tips.",
